At the beginning of the birth of living beings, [all things are animistic] and can absorb the spiritual energy of heaven and earth for cultivation. 
The monk was not afraid of heaven and earth, he searched high and low, and once challenged the rules of "Heaven", which led to its suppression! Since then, Heaven has imprinted the "Life Lock" on all living beings. Since birth, the longevity, talent, and cause and effect of mortal creatures have been bound by the "Life Lock". Even when they break through the realm, they will rain down "infinite calamities" in an attempt to kill those who violate the rules! However, there are fifty avenues and forty-nine heavenly evolutions. Humans can escape one of them. This one turns into "three thousand avenues", leaving a way for the creatures of heaven and earth to ascend to heaven. 
Monks all over the world are looking for a way, trying to break free from the chains of life, realize the way for themselves, "ascend to the upper world", and transcend reincarnation. 
After ascension, I discovered that the so-called heavenly way was just some kind of restriction set by man, and I was involved in a bigger dispute...🔥 Zero-pressure Cultivation of Immortality·Hook Up to Prove the Way 
●Vertical screen with one hand to control the overall situation: building caves, harvesting spiritual fields, tempering magic weapons, and control the world with one finger; 
●Cultivation of cultivation across time and space: offline automatic cultivation, a hundred years of retreat is equal to one day in real life, and a hundred years of cultivation will be accumulated when you wake up; 
●Upgrade with the thrill of realm jump: Body refining→Foundation building→Golden elixir→Nascent Soul... Every time you break through a level of heaven, you unlock magical powers, secret techniques, cave heaven and blessed land, and you can break the void after ascending to transcend tribulations. 🔥 Interaction between Taoists and help them ascend 
●Double cultivation method builds immortality together: Lingxi meets the moon, travels together in the immortal palace, the mind and Dharma are in harmony, the two hearts are in harmony and together they can overcome all tribulations; 
●Interactive blessings help your cultivation soar: a contract is formed for three lives, a Taoist couple can achieve enlightenment in one day, but alone can achieve enlightenment in ten years; 
●Advanced fairy fate and join hands to achieve immortality: First acquaintance → Heartbreak → Falling in love → Tie the knot. Each time you advance to a new level of love, you will unlock different interactive scenes and plots. Only when your love is deeply rooted can you embark on the journey to immortality together. 🔥Vientiane cultivation·immerse yourself in the path of immortality 
●Destiny is in your own hands and goes against the will of heaven: Five elements of thunder tribulation, inner demon test, nine levels of heavenly punishment... Every tribulation requires the coexistence of opportunity and strength, and the dynamic fate rewrites the path of immortality in real time; 
●Multi-dimensional growth paths: Kung Fu, puppet secrets, magic weapons, spiritual pets, and Taoist companions are all linked together, and can be freely combined to create an exclusive fighting style; 
●Open exploration map: Opportunities are triggered while strolling in the courtyard - encountering hidden masters, snatching treasures of heaven and earth, or even falling into the inner demon world. Every decision has hidden cause and effect. 🔥The universe accepts emptiness·All things can be refined 
●Elixir fire can create mysteries at will: every time the furnace is opened, there will be a random chaotic reaction. The conflict of medicinal properties may produce poisonous and evil elixirs, and the changes in the elixir patterns will also lead to the discovery of ancient elixir recipes; 
●All things are exhaled and refined: the heaven and earth are the flow of yin and yang in the house, the rhythm of exhaling and inhaling coincides with the movement of the sky, and the rhythm of breathing coincides with the ancient treasure-hunting techniques. Every time you meditate, the blind box will be opened. 🔥Rise of the sect·Confrontation among the three realms 
●Make friends with Taoists at your fingertips: Chat about your experiences on the world channel, use jade slips to discuss Taoism and resolve doubts, so you are never alone on the path of spiritual practice; 
●Gather immortal friends to form an immortal alliance: swipe left to collect the secret orders of the sect, swipe right to view the list of disciples, and take control of a sect with thousands of people with one movement of your spiritual consciousness; 
●Sword techniques bring thousands of swords back to the sect: sword cultivators form an array to draw thunder, talisman cultivators transform into dragons to protect the formation, pill fire burns the sky to cut off the enemy's retreat, and the immortal alliance breaks through the sky together. May all the immortal friends in this world create a life script that is more exciting than the hot search! !

