"Atana" was born out of taptap's Spotlight 21-Day Creation Challenge, and unexpectedly received support from a large number of players. With excitement and trepidation, we gradually came up with the idea of ​​making it into a complete game. Due to time constraints in the competition version, there were jumping plots, missing functions, inexplicable bugs, and the inability to support some devices... We are very grateful to the players for their tolerance, and we are determined to make a more perfect work. 
Now is our first step: we have submitted the content of the demo version to participate in the New Product Festival on Steam. On February 23, the new demo version of "Atana" will be available to play for free! In the trial version of "Atana", we have added or modified the following content: 
1. The story plot has been rearranged to give players a more complete emotional development with Atana, as well as clearer GB-oriented content. The new plot reaches more than 40,000 words; 
2. An ending illustration system has been added, allowing players to quickly check the triggered endings and triggering conditions (the game has a total of 10 endings, including a hidden ending~ Although in the trial version, players experience the opening plot of the game and cannot trigger any ending, but we have already implemented the function); 
3. Added Atana's attribute system, including mood value, intimacy, trust, and dependence, so that you can more intuitively see the changes in Xiaota's mentality (a secret note, these values ​​will be directly related to the triggering of the ending); 
4. Replaced with new original music; 
5. Added mac adaptation; 
6. When crowdfunding support reaches a certain amount, full English dubbing and multi-language support will be added to Atana (if support is sufficient, we will also add dubbing and localization in more languages as appropriate). 
In addition, we are also preparing a mobile version, but due to the difficulty of applying for a version number, we hope everyone will be more patient... (meaning that this matter may take a year or two to start) (sliding kneeling) 
The development of the full version requires the power of every lover, please support Xiaota! ! !
